. 10 . .

##   10 
aboard.by.nation.element.top10 <-
aboard.by.nation.element |>
  group_by() |>
  summarise(sum = sum()) |>
  arrange(desc(sum)) |>
  top_n(10)

aboard.by.nation.element.top10 |>
  ggplot(aes(x = , y = sum)) +
  geom_col(fill = 'dark blue') +
  geom_text(aes(x = , y = sum, label = sum), vjust = -0.5) + 
  theme_minimal() + 
  labs(title = '  Top 10', y = '')

(odered factor) .

aboard.by.nation.element.top10$ <- fct_reorder(aboard.by.nation.element.top10$, desc(aboard.by.nation.element.top10$sum))

plot.aboard.by.nation <- 
aboard.by.nation.element.top10 |>

  theme_minimal() +
